data.description: Welcome to beautiful Oswego. Presenting a spacious CORNER LOT 4-bedroom, 3.1-bath home boasting over 2,500 sq. feet of living space on a sizable fenced lot. Stepping through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting 2-story Entryway leading to the combined Living Room and Dining Room, adorned with beautiful wood flooring. The Kitchen seamlessly connects to the Family Room, creating an ideal space for indoor and outdoor entertaining. The Kitchen features a large island, a Bay Window with storage, and convenient pull-out shelves in the cabinets and newer appliances from 2021. Upstairs, three generously sized Bedrooms, two full Baths, and a versatile nook perfect for an office or reading corner await, providing a peaceful escape from the ground floor.  The fully FINISHED basement offers a rare find-a full bathroom and an additional BEDROOM, totaling four in this well-maintained home. Water heater 2023, roof is from 2020 and solar panels from 2023. Conveniently located near Downtown Oswego and major shopping areas, this home falls within WALKING DISTANCE of the highly regarded Oswego 308 school district. With its move-in ready condition and desirable features, this residence is not to be missed!
